These who can calculate ?
what powers of mind Scan their light textures, or their woof unfold ?
Thus proved attenuate, mark, benignant, next, Their keen rapidity:
with what vast speed Fleet they through ether, with elastic wing Conquering dull time, urged various to their goals.
This shall the muse in melodies evince
